OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAn unsettled
OL,6,Fevening in the east with showers and
OL,7,Fthunderstorms likely. Drier further
OL,8,Fwest. Turning more settled overnight
OL,9,Fwith some cloud breaks developing.
OL,10,FFurther showers crossing later in the
OL,11,Fnight. Temperatures remaining warm
OL,12,Fwith light southwesterly winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FFresher conditions spreading
OL,15,Fto all parts into Sunday. Cloudy at
OL,16,Ftimes with some sunny spells during
OL,17,Fthe afternoon. Winds moderate
OL,18,Fsouthwesterly and noticeably breezy
OL,19,Fnear coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
